    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] pants, those lady from my town, she advised me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But whatever possession I had before, she sold it from black market.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she bought me a watch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She said with the watch, if a Ukraine is karbovanets, and Romania is liras, and Russia is rubles, so with the watch, you always can sell it and get the currency, the right currency.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I took her advice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she really did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know if she made profit or not, but she used to sell for me to sell thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She bought me a watch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This watch saved me, because the policeman took up [INAUDIBLE] watch was like possessions, like millions.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But nobody had watches during the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he start playing with the-- with the arrows.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They fall down in the store.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was looking for the arrow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "As I'm start to putting down the pants, I put up the pants and I jumped the window.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I escaped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, And I escaped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I escaped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I go and seem out of town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm running, and those guys, what they gave me out, they were following me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they come on, come on, Andre.",
